pullRequest.body:
Use [Ideal.LiesOver](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/RingTheory/Ideal/Over.html#Ideal.LiesOver) in the results about [Ideal.inertiaDeg](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/NumberTheory/RamificationInertia.html#Ideal.inertiaDeg) in the case `[Algebra R S]`.

- [x] depends on: #18249
